            "block_label": "figure_title",
            "block_content": "Extended Data Fig. 4 | Expression, purification and activity measurement of selected de-novo-designed luciferases for h-CTZ. a, Coomassie-stained SDS-PAGE of HTZ3-D2 and HTZ3-G4 purified from recombinant expression in E. coli. b, Magnified views of HTZ3-D2 (left panel) and HTZ3-G4 (right panel) illustrated the side-chain preorganization of luciferase-h-CTZ interactions. c, d, Size-exclusion chromatography (left), deconvoluted mass spectrum (middle), and the normalized luciferase activities on selected compounds",
